#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/index.md:17
msgid ""
"**[Rust Guidelines](rust-guidelines/index.html)** — Rust-specific guidance "
"for naming, language items, and cross-cutting topics."
msgstr ""

#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/index.md:20
msgid ""
"**[Git Guidelines](git-guidelines.md)** — Commit hygiene and pull-request "
"conventions."
msgstr ""

#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/index.md:22
msgid ""
"**[Testing Guidelines](testing-guidelines.md)** — Test behavior, assertions, "
"regression policy, and cleanup."
msgstr ""

